OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScotland's new smoke alarms
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flaw comes into force       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A new law requiring every home in      
OL,6, Scotland to have interlinked smoke     
OL,7, alarms has come into force.            
OL,9,FThe Scottish government has said people
OL,10,Fwill not be penalised if they need more
OL,11,Ftime to install the alarms.            
OL,13,FBut opposition parties have called for 
OL,14,Fthe scheme to be delayed and said the  
OL,15,Fnew legislation had not been properly  
OL,16,Fpublicised.                            
OL,18,FScottish ministers have rejected the   
OL,19,Fcalls and given more money to help     
OL,20,Fvulnerable people install the alarms.  
OL,23,D]G     From the BBC News Website       
